Vibrational entropy               ...      0.02836370 Eh     17.80 kcal/mol
Rotational entropy                ...      0.01598559 Eh     10.03 kcal/mol
Translational entropy             ...      0.02025338 Eh     12.71 kcal/mol
-----------------------------------------------------------------------
Final entropy term                ...      0.06460267 Eh     40.54 kcal/mol

